<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"categories":["pdplibre"],"patternName":"core/block/235","name":"FAQ Section"},"align":"full","style":{"spacing":{"padding":{"right":"var:preset|spacing|50","left":"var:preset|spacing|50","top":"var:preset|spacing|80","bottom":"var:preset|spacing|80"},"blockGap":"var:preset|spacing|50","margin":{"top":"0","bottom":"0"}}},"backgroundColor":"ti-accent-secondary","layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->
